OL,4,CBank of England governor defends self
OL,5,Cover scandal
OL,6, Bank of England governor Andrew Bailey
OL,7, has defended himself after a former
OL,8, appeal court judge criticised evidence
OL,9, he gave to MPs over a scandal in which
OL,10, thousands lost their life savings.
OL,12,FMr Bailey is the former boss of the
OL,13,FFinancial Conduct Authority (FCA).
OL,15,FHe has been criticised by Dame
OL,16,FElizabeth Gloster for his role at the
OL,17,FFCA in regulating London Capital &
OL,18,FFinance, which collapsed in 2019.
OL,20,FMr Bailey said responsibility and
OL,21,Fculpability were not the same thing.
